{
  "stem": "13238.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And each and every one was pushing in, pushing in, for the whole night.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "That's how we survived the first five nights.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "The fifth night, we heard somebody came in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And they sending out the 801 men to Brunnlitz.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "They packed us in again, in cattle wagons.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And Brunnlitz is the same thing-- in Sudetenland, not far, where Oskar Schindler was born.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "He was born in the city called Zwittau.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And took us-- I don't remember how long.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "But couldn't take long, because Gross-Rosen, from Zwittau or Brunnlitz, is not far.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "Took us maybe a day.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "When we arrived, on the platform, on the train station, on a side, was standing a tall man-- I saw him the first time in my life-- with the Tyrol, Tyrol hat with a feather.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "It was Oskar Schindler with the SS people, who were transporting us to the camp of Brunnlitz.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "This was the camp what we were working from, approximately the 21st-- when we arrived to Brunnlitz-- till the liberation day of 9 of May, 1945.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "During those days, first of all, the food improved immediately, because everybody got a bigger ration.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "We got coffee.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "We got soap, what was really something what didn't exist in our [LAUGHS] language anymore.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "One day Oskar Schindler came.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "And this was just before the High Holidays.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "Came to the working place.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "And he ask everybody to close the doors from the outside, from our people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "And he had a speech to us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "He said, I know your holidays are coming up now.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "And I will try to give you whatever possible, in-- in order to rejoice the holidays.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "Something like that, many of us didn't hear for many years from a German, from a Nazi.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "Because whatever it is, he was still a Nazi.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
